quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  92,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  92,1,qasam hai raat ki jabkay woh chhaa jaye
  92,2,aur din ki jabkay woh roshan ho
  92,3,aur uss zaat ki jis ne nar aur madah ko peda kya
  92,4,dar haqeeqat tum logon ki koshishen mukhtalif qisam ki hain
  92,5,to jis ne ( raah khuda mein ) maal diya aur ( khuda ki nafarmani se ) parhaiz kya
  92,6,aur bhalai ko sach maana
  92,7,is ko hum aasaan rastay ke liye sahoolat den ge
  92,8,aur jis ne bukhal kya aur ( apne khuda se ) be nayazi Barti
  92,9,aur bhalai ko jhtlaya
  92,10,is ko hum sakht rastay ke liye sahoolat den ge
  92,11,aur uss ka maal aakhir uss ke kis kaam aeye ga jabkay woh halaak ho jaye ?
  92,12,be shak rasta batana hamaray zimma hai
  92,13,"aur dar haqeeqat akhirat aur duniya, dono ke hum hi maalik hain"
  92,14,pas mein ne tum ko khabardaar kar diya hai bharakti hui aag se
  92,15,uss mein nahi jhulsAYga magar woh intahi bud- bakht
  92,16,jis ne jhtlaya aur mun phera
  92,17,aur uss se daur rakha jaayegaa woh nihayat parhaizgaar
  92,18,jo pakeeza honay ki khatir apna maal deta hai
  92,19,uss par kisi ka koi ahsaan nahi hai jis ka badla ussay dena ho
  92,20,woh to sirf apne Rab bartar ki Raza joi ke liye yeh kaam karta hai
  92,21,aur zaroor woh ( uss se ) khush hoga
